{"tid":854173,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人]想揾返今日两點同我一樣係十樓岀𨋢嘅女仔","createTime":"2018-10-09T07:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T09:22:13.000Z","uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"616fce59cd7415486396627d3d75d87864c08f5f","tid":854173,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:42:05.000Z","msg":"雖然我連你有冇上連登都唔知 但我都係想試下喺到睇下揾唔揾到你<br />\n<br />\n話說今日大概2點我食完飯就如常上返位於新蒲崗某工廠大廈返工。我㩒完10樓正當𨋢門就關嘅時候我哨到有人沖緊埋黎想入𨋢，咁我就緊係即刻㩒返開門俾你入啦。跟住就見到著住深藍色T-shirt 淺藍色牛仔褲嘅你。<br />\n<br />\n你同我一齊係10樓岀左𨋢之後我就向右行而你就向左，正當我打開門入公司個下我轉頭向後諗住望多你最後一眼嘅時候，發現你都做緊同一樣嘅動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係咁我地對望左半秒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你有上連登嘅就係到同我say個hi啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者只係我毒撚FF太多嘅你都可以唔洗理我由呢個po沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834a777498e421d8568695fb8ae176de7b0f9fa9","tid":854173,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"死毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f04bad18dc4cf97d1f34a7a3f92f0fdbd72d8a","tid":854173,"uid":147710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"834a777498e421d8568695fb8ae176de7b0f9fa9","tid":854173,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"死毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"Sorry lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee93d3e35cb3ed0aadab8818e06d854df64d8142","tid":854173,"uid":63394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:44:46.000Z